name: Sunflower Synesthesia
description: This generative audiovisual composition is part of the series Minimal Mandala. The algorithm builds on foundational mandala grids inspired by ancient SE Asian structures. The base soundtrack is a direct sonification of each frame of the video by mapping its image data to audio frequency spectrum, creating a synesthetic link between image and sound in the process. 1080px x 1080px. 41s. Mp4. By @zenaranya.
